{"tid":1605262,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期至頂] 連登熄燈問題","createTime":"2019-09-30T08:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:58:43.000Z","uid":24577,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"84cc0560949e5f10f16118c278cb44bdc3f71fda","tid":1605262,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:38:35.000Z","msg":"各位，監於連登呢幾日不斷熄燈既問題，各位要有共識。我好相信10.1既時候會再熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我身邊重有好多人 連登一熄左登 就咩都唔知！<br />\n<br />\n記住，連登一熄登，唔好去Reddit，Reddit由於紅底 好大機會會封鎖晒啲消息！<br />\n<br />\n重要野要講三次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連登熄燈第一時間去twitter集中討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登熄燈第一時間去twitter集中討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登熄燈第一時間去twitter集中討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n使用 #lihkg/#LIHKG 或者兩個都Tag晒 為主要既Hashtag<br />\n<br />\n即時戰況既 可以加埋 #lihkglive 咁大家搵hashtag既時候會易啲<br />\n<br />\n我見到有人建議係用日期做hashtag 但我個人覺得Hashtag集中啲 會易啲用<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩建議 好快啲係下次熄燈前提出！<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a458760cf4d566e7bac1c7f8cc4513203e5ec19d","tid":1605262,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"yes. <br />\n無錯"},{"pid":"b5c77e5085609f3e5baf06979027cb73fc2c7a54","tid":1605262,"uid":24577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推 記住唔係因為有連登先有連登仔 係因為有連登仔所以先有連登！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1da7b331f069a10067672b9bd9c56faf3802bf58","tid":1605262,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:40:21.000Z","msg":